Installing OpenTrafficShaper:


*
* Requirements for OpenTrafficShaper
*

- POE
Debian: libpoe-perl

- Config::IniFiles
Debian: libconfig-inifiles-perl

- DateTime
Debian: libdatetime-perl

- Digest::SHA
Debian: libdigest-sha-perl

- JSON
Debian: libjson-perl

- Perl 5.6+


1. Copy opentrafficshaper to /usr/local/sbin/

